<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Kontakt – HUI</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: #050505;
      color: #f5f5f5;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      padding: 2rem 5vw;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    .logo {
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #00eaff;
    }

    main {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3rem 5vw 5rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .pill {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00eaff, #ff00c8);
      color: #050505;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    p {
      color: #d4d4d4;
      margin: 0.6rem 0;
    }

    form {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      display: grid;
      gap: 1.4rem;
    }

    input, textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1rem;
      outline: none;
      transition: border 0.2s ease;
    }

    input:focus, textarea:focus {
      border-color: #00eaff;
    }

    textarea {
      min-height: 140px;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    button {
      padding: 0.9rem 1.4rem;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00eaff, #ff00c8);
      color: #050505;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
    }

    button:hover {
      opacity: 0.85;
    }

    .info {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      padding-top: 2rem;
    }

    .info p {
      margin: 0.3rem 0;
    }

    a {
      color: #00eaff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <div class="logo">HUI · Human United Intelligence</div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <span class="pill">Kontakt</span>
    <h1>Wir sind für dich da</h1>
    <p>
      Du hast Fragen zu HUI, möchtest ein Projekt starten oder mit uns zusammenarbeiten?
      Schreib uns einfach – wir melden uns so schnell wie möglich.
    </p>

    <form>
      <input type="text" placeholder="Dein Name" required />
      <input type="email" placeholder="Deine E‑Mail" required />
      <textarea placeholder="Deine Nachricht" required></textarea>
      <button type="submit">Nachricht senden</button>
    </form>

    <div class="info">
      <h2>Weitere Kontaktmöglichkeiten</h2>
      <p>E‑Mail: <a href="mailto:info@hui-app.com">info@hui-app.com</a></p>
      <p>Website: <a href="https://hui-app.com">hui-app.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
